{"id": 2123, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，什么培养了你的进食习惯？", "description": "关于“吃什么”和“怎么吃”这种大问题，你都是如何做决定的？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 1457, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180115174044bzPTMCAGq7nyvf9j.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-17T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 259328, "content": "开始运动健身之后为了巩固成果控制饮食", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 259840, "content": "大概是身体出现问题后的迫不得已吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240384}, {"id": 260096, "content": "身体健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241476}, {"id": 262657, "content": "不知道吃什么的时候我连着吃了一个星期的黄焖鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 259330, "content": "周围有便利店之后不知道吃什么的时候有了备选项", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 259842, "content": "学校食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086466}, {"id": 259843, "content": "心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185044}, {"id": 259844, "content": "甜的。偏好苦味咖啡和巧克力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999723}, {"id": 259845, "content": "大学生活只能通过价钱来决定你的饮食，影响了之前在家所养成的饮食习惯。无奈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194606}, {"id": 259847, "content": "…其实有点受老妈健康饮食影响，开始根据身体状况吃东西，感冒着凉喝羊汤，上火了就吃沙拉，平时吃东西荤素搭配，只吃一种菜就会很不习惯，吃垃圾食品会有愧疚感…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 259848, "content": "饭馆首选离我近的，有一家已经赢得了我的心，他们有新品会请我试吃，我把他们的地址加到了百度地图里…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 259849, "content": "薄荷健康(APP)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240409}, {"id": 259850, "content": "除了米饭?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240417}, {"id": 264461, "content": "懒得出门去食堂打包，又客气到不好意思叫室友打包，毅然养成了定外卖的hao习惯?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 24797}, {"id": 260366, "content": "看心情", "image": "img/option/option/20180119192259hb15ETlndvP9UxRp", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227198}, {"id": 262674, "content": "边玩游戏边吃饭吃吃婷婷，导致正常吃饭吃会儿就累 需要休息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 259860, "content": "吃饭太快，而且老是把自己吃撑...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772496}, {"id": 259861, "content": "喝热水ui", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852595}, {"id": 261400, "content": "上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244453}, {"id": 260633, "content": "睡眠时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241169}, {"id": 260636, "content": "Ok", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237451}, {"id": 260638, "content": "水果占饮食的30%", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242800}, {"id": 262431, "content": "吃素，基本上不用烦恼吃什么，有的吃就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236789}, {"id": 262176, "content": "钱包余额", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247779}, {"id": 259874, "content": "吃还是不吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240438}, {"id": 259876, "content": "为了减肥多喝水多吃水果", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240440}, {"id": 259878, "content": "理智情况下：三大营养素的配比\n饿昏头馋晕时：想怎么吃怎么吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204352}, {"id": 259879, "content": "为了多活几年，一餐不落，营养均衡，该咋咋滴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236229}, {"id": 259880, "content": "懒.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187084}, {"id": 259881, "content": "坚持规律健身，让我可以「放开吃」~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516789}, {"id": 262186, "content": "现在吃东西能吃就行，要什么自行车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103848}, {"id": 259882, "content": "总想吃点肉，又没钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238610}, {"id": 259883, "content": "拥有想变瘦的心，吃了易长肉的食物！很无奈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240466}, {"id": 259884, "content": "总是吃同样的食物 同样的口味 懒得换", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835746}, {"id": 260396, "content": "母亲生病之后吧。再加上想瘦下来想有好皮肤，去欧洲交换有了自己做饭的机会，开始好好养生，不是朋克养生啊是真的少盐少油少主食，多吃素多吃粗粮。虽然我今年才二十岁…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242009}, {"id": 259885, "content": "看心情！平时进食只是为了活命！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239563}, {"id": 259886, "content": "口感，饥饿感，时间规律", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239112}, {"id": 259887, "content": "随缘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239590}, {"id": 259888, "content": "腾讯免费的早餐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758502}, {"id": 259889, "content": "运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238628}, {"id": 259890, "content": "爸妈给什么就吃什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239594}, {"id": 259891, "content": "喜欢的人的习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194347}, {"id": 260659, "content": "初高中都是重点学校，学习时间特别赶，所以吃饭都特别赶，就养成了快速吃饭的习惯，而且吃得又多又快。吃饭不说话不看剧，同学讲我吃饭的时候很严肃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930922}, {"id": 259892, "content": "超市特价，菜市场的远近，没洗的碗和没洗的锅，门口的面条店老板聊不聊的来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240521}, {"id": 259893, "content": "看学校餐厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225852}, {"id": 259895, "content": "生活节奏及money", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726744}, {"id": 263480, "content": "男朋友啊！ 租房一起住，他超爱吃锅塌豆腐，光想每顿都吃！得亏我没有那么讨厌豆腐，每次都说又是豆腐啊，不要了吧。等他做好了端出来闻着还是一如既往的美味，就又吃豆腐了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253727}, {"id": 259896, "content": "有几样喜欢吃的东西，然后每餐轮流吃这几样?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240556}, {"id": 259897, "content": "我认为，吃什么和怎么吃就像‘需要’和‘想要’的关系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240563}, {"id": 260665, "content": "体重增长带来的亚健康状态，还有肥胖引起的潜在疾病，最重要的是无法忍受难看的自己，通过半年的减肥，改变了以往的饮食习惯，减掉26斤！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135208}]}